<p><a name="Combining_ancient_and_modern_traditions" id="Combining_ancient_and_modern_traditions"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Stained_glass&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Combining ancient and modern traditions">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Combining ancient and modern traditions</span></h3>
